{
  "_metadata": {
    "name": "Public Repo Code & IaC Risk Triage",
    "description": "Authorized bug bounty workflow that extracts bounded source and IaC files from a public GitHub repository, runs Semgrep, Checkov, and Trivy repo checks, and writes a prioritized code risk report.",
